task.summary: * Instagram migrate to Instagram Graph API * Facebook API fixed to V3.1
* WebView navigation visibility fix * WebView file download permission fix
WebView navigation visibility fix follow up
Migrated to Tumblr API V2 with API key
Removed deprecated imports Fix for null radio metadata
Intents to HolderActivity via MainActivity now go directly to HolderActivity
* Drawer updated style * Increased Picasso, CompileSDK and SupportLib versions
WC Login Activity theme, JetPack provider thumbnail quality increase
Added new row layouts, switchable viewmodes and pull to refresh to WP, YT & RSS
Dynamic Elevation. Toolbar Elevation is hidden when not scrolled for certain fragments in light mode
Improved WooCommerce Layout Products can be filtered on sale and featured Only purchasable products are requested
SoundCloud provider now supports audio from both SoundCloud and Wordpress
Dynamic WooCommerce headers on home page
Open Source licenses in Preferences Bugfixes (soundcloud & woo)
Basic Auth for WooCommerce now supports url-based authentication also (rather than only header based) Lint error fix
Reversed Wordpress Audio parameter order to match wordpress
Confirmation before visiting site with non-verified SSL
Theming of menu icons in detail activity without header image fixed
Made forgotten Share string translateable in Strings.xml
